Fig. 17F
); middle portion with several pits (
Fig. 17F
); apex setose (
Fig. 17F
). Segment X of anal tube (
Fig. 17
G–H) longer than wide at widest portion; caudal margin (
Fig. 17G
) pointed with apex rounded; setose.
